# ABAC × SpiceDB (server) — CEL caveat `doc_attrs`
# Document attributes (incl. region) are STATIC caveat context (written at seed time); the
# principal's clearance/division/region MUST be supplied at check time (SpiceDB cannot look up
# subject attrs). Same dataset/IDs as cedar.abac.http — decisions must match.

@host = http://localhost:8080
@spicedb = http://localhost:8443
@key = benchkey

### ALLOW — via facade (context = the persona's TRUE attributes)
POST {{host}}/v1/authorize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "engine": "spicedb",
  "model": "abac",
  "principal": "psn-337717",
  "action": "doc.read",
  "resource_type": "AbacDocument",
  "resource": "adoc-0000413",
  "context": { "clearance": 2, "principal_division": "finance", "principal_region": "denpasar" }
}

### DENY — via facade (attribute / region mismatch)
POST {{host}}/v1/authorize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "engine": "spicedb",
  "model": "abac",
  "principal": "psn-1124199",
  "action": "doc.read",
  "resource_type": "AbacDocument",
  "resource": "adoc-0000321",
  "context": { "clearance": 3, "principal_division": "operations", "principal_region": "surabaya" }
}

### RAW — SpiceDB HTTP gateway with caveat context
POST {{spicedb}}/v1/permissions/check
Authorization: Bearer {{key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "consistency": { "fullyConsistent": true },
  "resource": { "objectType": "abac_document", "objectId": "adoc-0000413" },
  "permission": "read",
  "subject": { "object": { "objectType": "persona", "objectId": "psn-337717" } },
  "context": { "clearance": 2, "principal_division": "finance", "principal_region": "denpasar" }
}
